<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٩٨ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6085">مُسَدَّدٌ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4195">عُبَيْدِ اللهِ: </a>أَخْبَرَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">عَبْدِ اللهِ: </a>أَنَّ النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> <span class="c2">«كَانَ يُرْكَزُ لَهُ الْحَرْبَةُ فَيُصَلِّي إِلَيْهَا»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>